168
00:10:35,737 --> 00:10:43,522
And when the delinquent taxpayer seeks a redemption, they only get a redemption once all those costs have been paid.

169
00:10:44,500 --> 00:10:55,651
The taxes under this revolving fund, the taxes and the interest would go into the general fund, and the costs would then come back to the treasurer, who could then use them to pursue other cases.

170
00:10:56,091 --> 00:11:05,040
